import React from 'react';
import {
  ProjectContainer, ProjectTitle, LinksContainer, LinkButton, 
  Description, DemonstrationContainer, StepsContainer, StepItem, 
  StepDescription, GifContainer, GifImage, 
  Highlight, Subtitle, LightParagraph, FlexRow, Card, PillBadge, 
  GradientButton, GradientContainer, DashedContainer, Divider, 
  EmphasisText, GlassCard, Tooltip, TypewriterText, ZigzagSeparator, TextMod,
  
  // Importing the new styled components
  GradientBackground, GradientText, HoverGradientShift, GradientBorder, AnimatedGradient,
  GradientMask, GradientScrollbar, GradientShadow, GradientIconFill,
  
  // Assuming some basic animations for shapes and others:
  CircleExpand, SquareRotate, TriangleTilt, StarPulse, PolygonJitter,
  ImageZoom, ImageGrayscaleToColor, ImageTilt,
  DynamicFont, FontFamilySwitcher, ColoredText, WeightedText, ItalicText,
  UnderlinedText, UpperCaseText, LowerCaseText, LetterSpacingText, LineHeightText,

} from './StyledComp';

// ... (The rest of the code remains largely unchanged.)


const dummyData = {
  title: "Sample Project",
  websiteLink: "http://example.com",
  githubLink: "http://github.com/sample",
  demoLink: "http://youtube.com/watch?v=demo",
  description: "This is a sample project description. It explains the purpose and functionality of the project in brief.",
  demonstration: [
    {
      description: "Step 1: User Registration",
      gifImage: "path/to/registration-demo.gif"
    },
    {
      description: "Step 2: User Login and Dashboard Overview",
      gifImage: "path/to/login-demo.gif"
    }
  ]
};

const Project = () => {
    const { title, websiteLink, githubLink, demoLink, description, demonstration } = dummyData;
  
    return (
      <Card> {/* Wrap the entire project in a card for better presentation */}
        <ProjectContainer>
          <FlexRow>
            <ProjectTitle><Highlight>{title}</Highlight></ProjectTitle>
            <PillBadge>NEW</PillBadge>
          </FlexRow>
  
          <GradientBackground>Sample Gradient Background</GradientBackground>
          <GradientText>Sample Gradient Text</GradientText>
          <HoverGradientShift>Hover over me</HoverGradientShift>
          <GradientBorder startColor="black" endColor="white">Sample Gradient Border</GradientBorder>
          <AnimatedGradient>Animated Gradient</AnimatedGradient>
          <GradientMask>Sample Gradient Mask</GradientMask>
          <GradientScrollbar>Gradient Scrollbar Content</GradientScrollbar>
          <GradientShadow>Sample Gradient Shadow</GradientShadow>
          <GradientIconFill>🌟</GradientIconFill>
  
          <CircleExpand>🔵</CircleExpand>
          <SquareRotate>■</SquareRotate>
          <TriangleTilt>▲</TriangleTilt>
          <StarPulse>⭐</StarPulse>
          <PolygonJitter>Polygon Jitter (Placeholder)</PolygonJitter>
  
          <ImageZoom src="path_to_sample_image.jpg" alt="Image Zoom"/>
          <ImageGrayscaleToColor src="path_to_sample_image.jpg" alt="Image Grayscale to Color"/>
          <ImageTilt src="path_to_sample_image.jpg" alt="Image Tilt"/>
  
          <DynamicFont>Dynamic Font</DynamicFont>
          <FontFamilySwitcher>Font Family Switcher</FontFamilySwitcher>
          <ColoredText>Colored Text</ColoredText>
          <WeightedText>Weighted Text</WeightedText>
          <ItalicText>Italic Text</ItalicText>
          <UnderlinedText>Underlined Text</UnderlinedText>
          <UpperCaseText>uppercase text</UpperCaseText>
          <LowerCaseText>LOWERCASE TEXT</LowerCaseText>
          <LetterSpacingText>Letter Spacing Text</LetterSpacingText>
          <LineHeightText>Line Height Text</LineHeightText>
  
          <GradientContainer> 
            <LinksContainer>
              <GradientButton href={websiteLink}>Website</GradientButton>
              <GradientButton href={githubLink}>GitHub</GradientButton>
              {demoLink && <GradientButton href={demoLink}>Demonstration</GradientButton>}
            </LinksContainer>
          </GradientContainer>
  
          <DashedContainer> 
            <Description>
              <TextMod size="1.2rem" color="#444" font="Verdana, sans-serif" weight="500">
                {description}
              </TextMod>
            </Description>
          </DashedContainer>
  
          {demonstration && (
            <DemonstrationContainer>
              <GlassCard> 
                <Subtitle>Demonstration:</Subtitle>
                <StepsContainer>
                  {demonstration.map((step, index) => (
                    <StepItem key={index}>
                      <StepDescription>
                        <TextMod type="italic">{step.description}</TextMod>
                      </StepDescription>
                      <GifContainer>
                        <GifImage src={step.gifImage} alt={`Demo for step ${index + 1}`} />
                      </GifContainer>
                    </StepItem>
                  ))}
                </StepsContainer>
              </GlassCard>
            </DemonstrationContainer>
          )}
          <Divider />
        </ProjectContainer>
      </Card>
    );
  };
  
  export default Project;
